1
00:00:07,317 --> 00:00:09,040
If you forget all about it,

2
00:00:09,450 --> 00:00:10,840
do you want me to remind you?

3
00:00:10,963 --> 00:00:12,600
You can't go soft on him.

4
00:00:12,766 --> 00:00:15,590
We still need insight info from Prince Tinnakorn.

5
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:17,560
You went to see Prince Tinnakorn?

6
00:00:18,947 --> 00:00:20,240
My people suspected that

7
00:00:20,300 --> 00:00:23,280
Phob could be a part of the group wanting a regime change.

8
00:00:23,363 --> 00:00:24,364
Are you sure?

9
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:26,881
Are you here to watch the drill?

10
00:00:27,102 --> 00:00:28,920
I need to check for preparation,

11
00:00:29,854 --> 00:00:31,960
in case someone plans to stir something up.

12
00:02:04,404 --> 00:02:05,405
Mr. Phobthee.

13
00:02:06,151 --> 00:02:07,152
Mr. Phobthee!

14
00:02:07,983 --> 00:02:08,984
Phob!

15
00:02:14,292 --> 00:02:15,308
What is it?

16
00:02:15,839 --> 00:02:18,188
- Did you hear what you just said?
- It was the truth.

17
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:21,788
The economy is going downhill and people are struggling.

18
00:02:22,050 --> 00:02:24,188
Instead, aristocrats do nothing about it.

19
00:02:24,219 --> 00:02:26,108
Everyone is trying to save the country.

20
00:02:26,148 --> 00:02:27,228
That is from your perspective.

21
00:02:27,828 --> 00:02:28,948
But in my perspective,

22
00:02:29,278 --> 00:02:30,708
it should have been done better,

23
00:02:30,986 --> 00:02:32,348
not waiting until people are dying from starvation.

24
00:02:32,387 --> 00:02:33,388
You need to stop talking!

25
00:02:33,396 --> 00:02:35,048
You do know that people could misunderstand you

26
00:02:35,097 --> 00:02:36,228
if they just hear what you said, don't you?

27
00:02:36,488 --> 00:02:37,988
You could be in danger.

28
00:02:40,911 --> 00:02:41,912
Why are you smiling?

29
00:02:46,356 --> 00:02:47,357
Hey,

30
00:02:48,322 --> 00:02:49,988
do you care about me?

31
00:02:51,156 --> 00:02:52,228
As a colleague.

32
00:02:57,972 --> 00:02:59,228
Right,

33
00:03:00,220 --> 00:03:03,308
I haven't received the schedule of royal family members who will attend the event.

34
00:03:04,028 --> 00:03:05,188
Where are they staying at?

35
00:03:06,398 --> 00:03:07,868
I can provide them protection.

36
00:03:09,498 --> 00:03:11,988
I told you that it wasn't your job.

37
00:03:36,562 --> 00:03:39,058
I saw the reaction of Kitti and Phob today,

38
00:03:39,148 --> 00:03:40,848
it was obvious of what they had in mind.

39
00:03:42,642 --> 00:03:45,908
They could be planning for the regime change.

40
00:03:49,408 --> 00:03:50,409
Dad?

41
00:03:51,036 --> 00:03:52,037
Actually,

42
00:03:53,111 --> 00:03:54,828
Phob asked me

43
00:03:55,068 --> 00:03:57,269
about the schedule for all royal family members.

44
00:03:58,023 --> 00:03:59,024
He did?

45
00:04:00,367 --> 00:04:01,548
Did you give it to him?

46
00:04:02,608 --> 00:04:03,609
I haven't.

47
00:04:03,968 --> 00:04:05,548
It wasn't his job.

48
00:04:07,228 --> 00:04:08,268
But Dad,

49
00:04:09,308 --> 00:04:12,509
I think perhaps he just felt oppressed

50
00:04:13,868 --> 00:04:16,028
that the country was in trouble,

51
00:04:16,464 --> 00:04:17,508
we're facing economic recession,

52
00:04:19,188 --> 00:04:22,108
I don't think he would do such thing.

53
00:04:29,156 --> 00:04:30,157
Tinnakorn,

54
00:04:31,684 --> 00:04:32,988
I need your help.

55
00:04:34,648 --> 00:04:35,649
Okay?

56
00:04:39,556 --> 00:04:41,308
The regime change?

57
00:04:43,968 --> 00:04:46,748
You dream big, you filthy slave.

58
00:04:51,372 --> 00:04:53,628
Do you remember our conversation

59
00:04:53,666 --> 00:04:55,548
before you left to study in England?

60
00:04:56,780 --> 00:04:58,268
Before I left for England?

61
00:04:59,746 --> 00:05:01,348
Before you left,

62
00:05:01,495 --> 00:05:05,068
you said that you'd talk to our fathers about our marriage.

63
00:05:05,559 --> 00:05:07,108
I remember it well.

64
00:05:08,226 --> 00:05:09,463
I remember it, too.

65
00:05:10,626 --> 00:05:12,588
If you don't want to marry me….

66
00:05:12,727 --> 00:05:14,908
You don't want to marry me either.

67
00:05:16,468 --> 00:05:17,548
I know

68
00:05:18,047 --> 00:05:19,748
that you don't love me.

69
00:05:19,994 --> 00:05:21,908
You love someone else.

70
00:05:28,367 --> 00:05:29,368
I'm sorry.

71
00:05:30,308 --> 00:05:32,108
You don't need to apologize.

72
00:05:32,951 --> 00:05:34,952
We don't love each other like that

73
00:05:35,436 --> 00:05:38,148
and we shouldn't be bonded by marriage.

74
00:05:38,908 --> 00:05:40,509
The problem is that

75
00:05:40,948 --> 00:05:43,548
I can't talk about this topic to my dad.

76
00:05:43,847 --> 00:05:45,508
He never listens to me.

77
00:05:47,908 --> 00:05:49,548
I understand.

78
00:05:51,148 --> 00:05:54,508
I will talk to my dad and our elderly relatives about this.

79
00:05:59,452 --> 00:06:00,453
Tinnakorn,

80
00:06:01,026 --> 00:06:03,668
even though we wont' be engaged anymore,

81
00:06:04,850 --> 00:06:08,948
I still love and care for you.

82
00:06:09,756 --> 00:06:12,308
If something is bothering you,

83
00:06:12,404 --> 00:06:14,068
whatever it is,

84
00:06:14,588 --> 00:06:16,748
please know that I will always be here for you.

85
00:06:16,807 --> 00:06:18,868
I will listen and help you through it.

86
00:06:19,703 --> 00:06:21,468
Thank you, Siri.

87
00:06:22,108 --> 00:06:24,448
I'm so lucky to have you as a lovely sister,

88
00:06:24,663 --> 00:06:27,028
who always means well and understands me.

89
00:06:31,546 --> 00:06:32,547
Hi, Phob.

90
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:35,141
Janthorn.

91
00:06:35,943 --> 00:06:37,588
Are you here for the garden festival?

92
00:06:38,316 --> 00:06:40,748
That's right, I want to put it in the news

93
00:06:40,852 --> 00:06:42,508
so I asked Phob to take me here.

94
00:06:52,346 --> 00:06:54,588
Phob, please take care of Tinnakorn.

95
00:07:22,948 --> 00:07:23,949
Follow me.

96
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:40,148
You look so happy today.

97
00:07:40,788 --> 00:07:42,148
Unlike the other day, you looked so gloomy.

98
00:07:43,508 --> 00:07:45,908
I'm happy because of you

99
00:07:45,954 --> 00:07:47,508
for giving me advice the other day.

100
00:07:49,770 --> 00:07:50,771
Wait,

101
00:07:52,394 --> 00:07:53,628
I thought a friend of your friend

102
00:07:53,690 --> 00:07:56,148
had that problem.

103
00:07:56,884 --> 00:08:00,588
Well, a friend of my friend wanted to say thank you to you.

104
00:08:18,727 --> 00:08:21,788
Have some cake, it's delicious.

105
00:09:17,088 --> 00:09:18,089
How is it? Delicious?

106
00:09:20,748 --> 00:09:21,749
Yeah.

107
00:09:26,239 --> 00:09:27,868
Why are you leading me here?

108
00:09:32,114 --> 00:09:33,388
What do you want?

109
00:09:37,068 --> 00:09:38,428
What are you doing?

110
00:09:38,796 --> 00:09:40,955
What? You asked me about what I wanted.

111
00:09:41,522 --> 00:09:43,068
This is what I want.

112
00:09:43,444 --> 00:09:45,108
Not this.

113
00:09:51,418 --> 00:09:52,419
It's about this.

114
00:09:57,218 --> 00:09:58,748
A schedule about

115
00:09:58,819 --> 00:10:00,508
all royal family members' arrival during the celebration.

116
00:10:06,746 --> 00:10:08,228
Why did you change your mind?

117
00:10:09,428 --> 00:10:11,668
You said that you wanted it for protection plan.

118
00:10:13,644 --> 00:10:15,508
Now that I gave it to you, it'd be over.

119
00:10:16,551 --> 00:10:18,748
And you should stop messing around me already.

120
00:10:38,255 --> 00:10:39,256
Phob!

121
00:10:42,068 --> 00:10:43,069
Prince Chatthorn?

122
00:10:46,698 --> 00:10:48,908
Oh, you still remember me?

123
00:10:49,699 --> 00:10:50,908
I thought you would forget about me.

124
00:10:59,263 --> 00:11:01,028
You're a Captain's mom now.

125
00:11:02,612 --> 00:11:04,628
And you might forget who you used to be.

126
00:11:06,594 --> 00:11:10,188
I'm grateful for all of your family members, I never forget any of you.

127
00:11:12,967 --> 00:11:14,388
You never forget?

128
00:11:17,047 --> 00:11:20,548
Why was your son

129
00:11:21,415 --> 00:11:23,788
so ungrateful to all of us?

130
00:11:25,628 --> 00:11:28,268
He is trying to destroy pride and honor of me and my people.

131
00:11:29,268 --> 00:11:30,588
What do you mean by that?

132
00:11:31,423 --> 00:11:32,708
What did Phob do?

133
00:11:36,108 --> 00:11:37,292
How could you ask me that?

134
00:11:37,392 --> 00:11:40,588
- Your son…
- You found out about Phob and your brother?

135
00:11:43,426 --> 00:11:44,427
Huh?

136
00:11:45,143 --> 00:11:46,144
Phob?

137
00:11:46,354 --> 00:11:47,355
And Tinnakorn?

138
00:11:50,898 --> 00:11:52,788
I tried to stop my son

139
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,028
from being around Prince Tinnakorn.

140
00:11:56,268 --> 00:11:58,428
He could taint the prince's reputation.

141
00:12:02,108 --> 00:12:03,628
What did he to to my brother?

142
00:12:08,068 --> 00:12:09,308
What did he to to my brother?

143
00:12:10,028 --> 00:12:11,508
What did he to to my brother?

144
00:12:12,450 --> 00:12:14,668
He did something to Tin that night, didn't he? What did he do?

145
00:12:14,738 --> 00:12:17,148
What did he do? What did he do to Tinnakorn?

146
00:12:17,172 --> 00:12:20,108
Tell me! I said tell me! Come on!

147
00:12:20,173 --> 00:12:22,028
Let her go! What are you doing to my mom?

148
00:12:22,828 --> 00:12:23,868
Phob!

149
00:12:25,367 --> 00:12:26,628
Mom!

150
00:12:27,378 --> 00:12:28,379
Mom!

151
00:12:30,204 --> 00:12:31,205
Mom!

152
00:12:32,364 --> 00:12:33,365
Mom!

153
00:12:33,692 --> 00:12:35,308
You took care of what I asked, right?

154
00:12:37,308 --> 00:12:38,309
I did.

155
00:12:40,586 --> 00:12:42,848
If he is a part of the rebellion,

156
00:12:43,738 --> 00:12:45,748
we will find out that day.

157
00:12:51,812 --> 00:12:52,813
Dad!

158
00:12:55,082 --> 00:12:58,028
About Phob's big attempt to transform the nation,

159
00:12:59,068 --> 00:13:01,028
don't you worry a thing.

160
00:13:01,391 --> 00:13:02,848
I handled it already.

161
00:13:03,468 --> 00:13:04,469
How did you know about this?

162
00:13:05,220 --> 00:13:06,221
What did you handle?

163
00:13:06,583 --> 00:13:09,070
I heard about what you and Tinnakorn said,

164
00:13:09,367 --> 00:13:11,498
so I threatened Nual and she passed out.

165
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:13,908
- I don't think he would…
- How much did you say to her?

166
00:13:15,668 --> 00:13:17,988
I didn't say anything much, she just passed out…

167
00:13:19,444 --> 00:13:20,245
Chat!

168
00:13:20,308 --> 00:13:22,548
You're not helping and you're causing more troubles!

169
00:13:23,194 --> 00:13:25,028
You're so good at stupid things!

170
00:13:26,698 --> 00:13:29,748
Why did you hit me? I was just trying to help.

171
00:13:30,015 --> 00:13:31,108
You? Helping?

172
00:13:31,183 --> 00:13:33,548
If you hadn't done anything,

173
00:13:33,584 --> 00:13:35,108
it would have been better for us.

174
00:13:35,316 --> 00:13:37,028
Now they know about plan

175
00:13:37,143 --> 00:13:39,188
and it was all ruined because of you.

176
00:13:40,588 --> 00:13:41,948
I started to wonder

177
00:13:42,002 --> 00:13:43,668
if you really were my son.

178
00:13:44,028 --> 00:13:46,508
Or someone switched you at birth with a calf!

179
00:13:46,543 --> 00:13:48,108
That's why you're so stupid like this!

180
00:13:49,924 --> 00:13:52,028
Get the hell out of my face! Go!

181
00:13:52,191 --> 00:13:53,668
I don't want to see your face anymore. Go!

182
00:13:54,748 --> 00:13:55,749
Chat.

183
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:13,920
Chat.

184
00:14:16,548 --> 00:14:19,268
Dad is still furious, please don't be mad at him.

185
00:14:23,308 --> 00:14:24,722
How could someone like me

186
00:14:26,775 --> 00:14:28,228
be mad at anyone?

187
00:14:29,042 --> 00:14:30,043
Chat.

188
00:14:35,108 --> 00:14:37,348
I'm stupid like a buffalo

189
00:14:38,602 --> 00:14:39,988
I shouldn't have been born as his son.

190
00:14:56,722 --> 00:14:57,653
But..

191
00:14:57,673 --> 00:14:59,730
you shouldn't have hurt Nual like that.

192
00:15:01,804 --> 00:15:03,394
You would just make it worse.

193
00:15:04,962 --> 00:15:07,108
Are you blaming me even more?

194
00:15:12,095 --> 00:15:13,096
That's right.

195
00:15:13,994 --> 00:15:14,995
I'm not you.

196
00:15:16,348 --> 00:15:17,349
- No!
- I did everything wrong.

197
00:15:20,215 --> 00:15:21,308
Since I was young,

198
00:15:24,236 --> 00:15:25,588
I can never be good at anything.

199
00:15:28,308 --> 00:15:29,708
I wasn't a good student.

200
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:34,268
I couldn't be as good as you were.

201
00:15:41,546 --> 00:15:42,547
Do you know

202
00:15:44,354 --> 00:15:46,355
how much I am jealous of you?

203
00:15:48,594 --> 00:15:50,948
Dad loves only you,

204
00:15:52,370 --> 00:15:53,788
he praises only you.

205
00:15:58,807 --> 00:15:59,868
And me…

206
00:16:02,348 --> 00:16:03,428
I'm not good at anything.

207
00:16:04,068 --> 00:16:05,948
Stop talking like that.

208
00:16:08,428 --> 00:16:09,748
Don't ever think like that.

209
00:16:10,888 --> 00:16:11,948
Stop thinking like that.

210
00:16:13,948 --> 00:16:15,668
You're also his son.

211
00:16:16,876 --> 00:16:18,068
Dad loves you.

212
00:16:19,308 --> 00:16:20,588
Dad loves you, okay?

213
00:16:20,628 --> 00:16:21,629
Not true.

214
00:16:23,448 --> 00:16:25,149
Trust me, he loves you.

215
00:16:27,154 --> 00:16:28,168
And I love you.

216
00:16:33,164 --> 00:16:34,188
You hear me?

217
00:16:34,988 --> 00:16:37,908
Dad loves you, I love you, everyone in this house loves you.

218
00:16:40,308 --> 00:16:41,509
We all love you.

219
00:16:49,439 --> 00:16:50,440
You understand?

220
00:16:53,695 --> 00:16:55,268
If you're not stop crying, I will tell Ruethaisiri.

221
00:16:56,628 --> 00:16:57,629
Will you stop crying?

222
00:17:02,277 --> 00:17:03,278
Good boy.

223
00:17:13,346 --> 00:17:15,748
She has suffered from heart disease.

224
00:17:16,151 --> 00:17:17,868
When she was terrifed about something,

225
00:17:18,063 --> 00:17:20,548
her heart works harder than usual.

226
00:17:20,927 --> 00:17:22,108
And it is dangerous.

227
00:17:23,055 --> 00:17:26,228
I'd suggest her to rest

228
00:17:26,668 --> 00:17:29,068
and avoid hearing news that could upset her.

229
00:17:32,727 --> 00:17:33,728
I understand.

230
00:17:34,447 --> 00:17:35,448
Thank you.

231
00:18:13,426 --> 00:18:14,788
What the hell is wrong with you?

232
00:18:15,311 --> 00:18:16,312
- Huh?
- What do you think?

233
00:18:19,220 --> 00:18:22,068
Do you know who I am? Do you?

234
00:18:22,548 --> 00:18:23,908
You're Prince Chatthorn.

235
00:18:42,826 --> 00:18:44,068
That's enough.

236
00:18:47,367 --> 00:18:48,388
Stop it.

237
00:19:01,264 --> 00:19:02,265
Phob?

238
00:19:04,386 --> 00:19:05,468
You slave!

239
00:19:06,519 --> 00:19:08,068
How dare you do this to me?

240
00:19:10,428 --> 00:19:11,429
What did I do?

241
00:19:14,188 --> 00:19:16,348
I'm here to help you.

242
00:19:21,124 --> 00:19:24,188
Why are you all still standing here?

243
00:19:27,244 --> 00:19:28,348
I'm sorry.

244
00:19:29,687 --> 00:19:30,688
Please go.

245
00:19:41,303 --> 00:19:42,304
See?

246
00:19:43,148 --> 00:19:44,748
I'm here to help you, really.

247
00:19:48,408 --> 00:19:49,409
Therefore,

248
00:19:50,628 --> 00:19:51,629
from now on,

249
00:19:53,018 --> 00:19:54,548
you need to behave, okay?

250
00:20:00,548 --> 00:20:02,549
Don't mess with my mom ever again.

251
00:20:14,028 --> 00:20:15,029
Come on.

252
00:21:03,514 --> 00:21:05,508
Nual! Pleae don't get up, please.

253
00:21:06,095 --> 00:21:07,096
Prince Tinnakorn?

254
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:12,578
Nual, I…

255
00:21:14,428 --> 00:21:15,428
I'm here to apologize.

256
00:21:17,588 --> 00:21:19,468
I'm apologizing for my brother.

257
00:21:20,700 --> 00:21:21,828
I'm really sorry.

258
00:21:21,895 --> 00:21:23,268
Your Highness,

259
00:21:24,226 --> 00:21:27,188
please don't do that, I'm not worth it.

260
00:21:32,402 --> 00:21:33,468
Did my brother

261
00:21:34,914 --> 00:21:36,388
say anything to you?

262
00:21:40,708 --> 00:21:43,148
He said that

263
00:21:44,448 --> 00:21:45,449
Phob was likely

264
00:21:46,879 --> 00:21:48,748
to ruin your reputation.

265
00:21:50,231 --> 00:21:52,268
Did he know about this?

266
00:21:52,855 --> 00:21:53,856
No, he didn't.

267
00:21:55,090 --> 00:21:56,091
It's not that.

268
00:21:58,551 --> 00:22:00,188
About that,

269
00:22:01,106 --> 00:22:02,628
besides about Phob and I,

270
00:22:03,588 --> 00:22:05,268
did he say something else?

271
00:22:06,789 --> 00:22:08,068
Something like..

272
00:22:09,428 --> 00:22:10,708
Phob's work?

273
00:22:11,548 --> 00:22:12,549
Or

274
00:22:13,290 --> 00:22:15,648
what is his plan?

275
00:22:17,508 --> 00:22:18,628
Did he say anything?

276
00:22:20,868 --> 00:22:21,948
No, I don't think so.

277
00:22:28,564 --> 00:22:29,708
Your Highness,

278
00:22:31,188 --> 00:22:32,189
from now on,

279
00:22:33,428 --> 00:22:34,868
I will stop my son

280
00:22:35,588 --> 00:22:38,028
not to be around you anymore.

281
00:22:39,188 --> 00:22:40,748
It is entirely my son's fault

282
00:22:41,148 --> 00:22:43,349
to cause all the mess.

283
00:22:44,124 --> 00:22:47,388
He was ungrateful for your family.

284
00:22:48,263 --> 00:22:50,508
Instead, he tried to

285
00:22:50,968 --> 00:22:53,388
- ruin your reputation.
- It's not his fault.

286
00:22:53,719 --> 00:22:55,868
Not true. It is his fault.

287
00:22:56,908 --> 00:22:58,388
It is Phob's fault.

288
00:22:59,276 --> 00:23:02,354
He dragged the sky to stoop to his level.

289
00:23:03,255 --> 00:23:05,448
He tried to run away from me.

290
00:23:07,042 --> 00:23:08,268
He really did.

291
00:23:14,162 --> 00:23:15,163
It was me.

292
00:23:15,826 --> 00:23:17,548
I pulled him closer to me.

293
00:23:21,948 --> 00:23:24,549
And it was me who left him.

294
00:23:29,703 --> 00:23:31,868
I caused you and Phob to leave the palace.

295
00:23:32,887 --> 00:23:35,948
I pushed both of you to struggle in life.

296
00:23:36,959 --> 00:23:39,508
I'm sorry. Please don't be mad at me.

297
00:23:39,620 --> 00:23:43,028
Oh my goodness, please don't say that.

298
00:23:44,588 --> 00:23:45,589
You know what?

299
00:23:46,804 --> 00:23:48,068
When I saw that

300
00:23:49,108 --> 00:23:51,348
Phob became Captain, I was so happy for him.

301
00:23:53,263 --> 00:23:54,828
I was happy to see that

302
00:23:56,036 --> 00:23:57,548
he was the same talented man that I knew.

303
00:24:01,428 --> 00:24:04,448
When I learned that after he left the palace,

304
00:24:06,029 --> 00:24:07,788
he struggled so much in his life.

305
00:24:10,228 --> 00:24:11,710
I wanted to praise him

306
00:24:12,829 --> 00:24:15,188
for his effort that he refused to give up.

307
00:24:17,788 --> 00:24:20,508
He is a soldier with bright future.

308
00:24:21,789 --> 00:24:24,308
I will never cause him any damage.

309
00:24:26,759 --> 00:24:27,948
I will never let him

310
00:24:30,028 --> 00:24:32,068
ruin his future because of me.

311
00:25:06,924 --> 00:25:09,628
My sources received the schedule of royal family members

312
00:25:10,316 --> 00:25:12,228
and it is the same information that you got.

313
00:25:12,487 --> 00:25:14,935
It is trustworthy.

314
00:25:15,991 --> 00:25:17,798
The royal ceremony will take place in the first couple of days.

315
00:25:19,980 --> 00:25:22,988
I think we should start our plan the next day

316
00:25:24,148 --> 00:25:26,788
when they arrive and gather up at the theater,

317
00:25:27,868 --> 00:25:29,308
according to their schedule.

318
00:25:30,468 --> 00:25:32,469
It will be easier to control them.

319
00:25:32,743 --> 00:25:33,744
I agree with your plan.

320
00:25:34,455 --> 00:25:37,428
Phobthee, you need to lead our team to that place

321
00:25:38,119 --> 00:25:40,868
and detain important members for negotiation.

322
00:25:46,918 --> 00:25:49,188
There will be no royal family members stay in that place.

323
00:25:50,308 --> 00:25:53,388
Our people will stay there and wait for the fight

324
00:25:53,508 --> 00:25:54,948
against the ungrateful traitors.

325
00:25:55,874 --> 00:25:57,428
We are digging up the pond

326
00:25:58,628 --> 00:26:00,348
and now we are waiting for fish to catch its bait.

327
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:08,840
[April 7, 1932]

328
00:26:41,892 --> 00:26:43,460
The royal ceremony in the first couples of days

329
00:26:43,663 --> 00:26:46,028
turned out to be so marvelous, Your Highness.

330
00:26:46,882 --> 00:26:48,788
People looked so happy and they enjoyed the ceremony.

331
00:26:51,618 --> 00:26:53,628
I hope it stays this way until the end.

332
00:26:57,986 --> 00:27:00,468
Did you hear what the King said the other day?

333
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:05,588
When people are happy in the country,

334
00:27:06,698 --> 00:27:09,228
the country will remain its peace.

335
00:27:11,156 --> 00:27:12,468
Our country

336
00:27:12,812 --> 00:27:15,828
has been a peaceful nation for 150 years.

337
00:27:17,913 --> 00:27:21,588
I hope that Siamese people will continue to live happily like this forever,

338
00:27:23,060 --> 00:27:25,788
with no traitors to ruin the peace of the nation.

339
00:27:56,058 --> 00:27:58,548
The important members are gathering up in one place, right?

340
00:27:59,988 --> 00:28:00,989
Yes, sir.

341
00:28:01,594 --> 00:28:04,188
My sources reported that if they'd start the mission,

342
00:28:04,506 --> 00:28:06,028
they would send someone to detain the members first.

343
00:28:06,618 --> 00:28:07,754
If that's the case,

344
00:28:08,095 --> 00:28:10,188
the leader should be a person who is close to Kitti,

345
00:28:10,775 --> 00:28:11,776
Captain Phobthee.

346
00:28:13,876 --> 00:28:16,628
If they break in, you can shoot them all.

347
00:28:24,164 --> 00:28:25,165
Dad?

348
00:28:25,787 --> 00:28:27,548
That's not what you said to me.

349
00:28:28,388 --> 00:28:29,908
You said that if

350
00:28:29,948 --> 00:28:32,028
Phob was involved with this, you'd get him out

351
00:28:32,058 --> 00:28:33,059
and you'd help him.

352
00:28:33,448 --> 00:28:36,268
If he started it, I needed to kill him.

353
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:40,628
Tinnakorn, you can't go soft on him.

354
00:29:52,191 --> 00:29:53,828
When you reach the destination, tell them to let me know.

355
00:30:05,130 --> 00:30:06,131
Excuse me,

356
00:30:06,628 --> 00:30:07,908
did you see Capt. Phobthee?

357
00:30:08,848 --> 00:30:11,028
He led the soldiers out of this place already.

358
00:30:13,468 --> 00:30:14,668
- He's gone?
- Yes, sir.

359
00:30:30,476 --> 00:30:31,477
Phob!

360
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,461
Phob!

361
00:30:34,567 --> 00:30:35,568
Phob!

362
00:30:39,906 --> 00:30:40,907
Phob!

363
00:30:43,682 --> 00:30:46,468
If they break in, you can shoot them all.

364
00:30:58,671 --> 00:30:59,828
Phob!

365
00:31:01,388 --> 00:31:02,389
Phob!

366
00:31:21,634 --> 00:31:22,635
Your Highness?

367
00:31:28,748 --> 00:31:29,749
Phob.

368
00:31:30,948 --> 00:31:31,949
Phob.

369
00:31:38,228 --> 00:31:39,428
Are you okay?

370
00:31:40,292 --> 00:31:42,788
You didn't ride in the car with the soldiers?

371
00:31:47,602 --> 00:31:50,468
They're done for the day

372
00:31:51,479 --> 00:31:52,908
so they are travelling back to their camps.

373
00:31:54,311 --> 00:31:58,028
What about the protection for aristocrats at the theatre?

374
00:31:58,428 --> 00:32:00,308
You didn't do it?

375
00:32:01,508 --> 00:32:02,638
About the security plan,

376
00:32:07,031 --> 00:32:09,148
the civil officials all agreed that

377
00:32:09,356 --> 00:32:11,988
we should postpone our mission, not to do it today.

378
00:32:12,948 --> 00:32:14,788
There are many people attending the celebration.

379
00:32:15,268 --> 00:32:16,669
It could lead to a bloodbath situation.

380
00:32:17,048 --> 00:32:18,828
I'll tell them to abort the mission.

381
00:32:42,844 --> 00:32:45,188
The Royal Guard has taken over the protection.

382
00:32:50,052 --> 00:32:51,053
It's okay.

383
00:32:53,199 --> 00:32:54,200
It's alright.

384
00:32:55,148 --> 00:32:56,149
I am here with you.

385
00:33:07,828 --> 00:33:09,308
I thought I would never see you again.

386
00:33:18,999 --> 00:33:20,000
Phob!

387
00:33:20,096 --> 00:33:22,148
Phob, you slave!

388
00:33:22,311 --> 00:33:23,468
Go to hell!

389
00:33:23,796 --> 00:33:24,797
Phob!

390
00:33:32,724 --> 00:33:34,284
Your Highness!

391
00:33:35,388 --> 00:33:36,389
Your Highness!

392
00:33:40,514 --> 00:33:42,828
Your Highness!

393
00:33:43,698 --> 00:33:44,699
Your Highness!

394
00:33:44,708 --> 00:33:45,828
Phob, are you okay?

395
00:33:55,548 --> 00:33:56,549
Your Highness!

396
00:33:57,308 --> 00:33:58,309
Your Highness!

397
00:33:59,524 --> 00:34:00,525
Your Highness!

398
00:34:04,263 --> 00:34:06,068
I am not dreaming, am I?

399
00:34:07,364 --> 00:34:08,368
You are dreaming

400
00:34:11,492 --> 00:34:12,628
and you will wake up soon.

401
00:34:58,244 --> 00:34:59,748
Chat is here.

402
00:34:59,844 --> 00:35:02,308
When will Tinnakorn be back?

403
00:35:03,268 --> 00:35:04,269
I don't know either.

404
00:35:04,708 --> 00:35:05,748
It is getting late.

405
00:35:06,468 --> 00:35:09,188
I haven't seen him since after the ceremony. I didn't know where he was.

406
00:35:22,298 --> 00:35:24,299
[Operating Room]

407
00:35:35,298 --> 00:35:36,428
How is he?

408
00:35:36,732 --> 00:35:38,148
He is doing fine.

409
00:35:38,487 --> 00:35:40,308
The bullet grazed his arm, it wasn't lodged in.

410
00:35:40,535 --> 00:35:42,268
I healed his would and it stopped bleeding.

411
00:35:42,700 --> 00:35:44,748
He passed out in the beginning because

412
00:35:44,801 --> 00:35:47,268
he was terrified and stressed out.

413
00:35:48,225 --> 00:35:49,226
Excuse me.

414
00:36:07,148 --> 00:36:08,149
Phob.

415
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,468
Phob, don't leave me.

416
00:36:10,967 --> 00:36:13,308
- Your Highness?
- Phob, don't go.

417
00:36:14,388 --> 00:36:15,389
Your Highness.

418
00:36:16,178 --> 00:36:18,628
I'm here. I'm standing right here.

419
00:36:20,828 --> 00:36:21,829
I'm right here with you.

420
00:36:30,244 --> 00:36:31,245
It's fine.

421
00:36:32,090 --> 00:36:33,091
It's going to be okay.

422
00:36:34,508 --> 00:36:36,228
Your Phob is right here with you.

423
00:36:38,168 --> 00:36:39,708
And I won't leave your side, ever.

424
00:37:07,108 --> 00:37:10,028
Dad, I don't think we should report a missing person to the police.

425
00:37:10,132 --> 00:37:12,266
Tinnakorn will come back soon. He might get drunk somewhere.

426
00:37:12,330 --> 00:37:14,333
Tinnakorn is not like you.

427
00:37:14,348 --> 00:37:15,988
He won't get too drunk to go home.

428
00:37:16,023 --> 00:37:18,028
There must be something happen to him.

429
00:37:22,802 --> 00:37:23,803
Phob?

430
00:37:28,756 --> 00:37:30,148
You should go.

431
00:37:30,239 --> 00:37:32,068
I'm fine.

432
00:37:32,748 --> 00:37:33,749
Tinnakorn?

433
00:37:34,370 --> 00:37:35,371
What happened to you?

434
00:37:39,105 --> 00:37:41,068
- What did you do?
- Dad!

435
00:37:41,308 --> 00:37:43,668
- What did you do to my son?
- Please, no.

436
00:37:44,482 --> 00:37:46,268
Please, don't hurt him.

437
00:37:46,588 --> 00:37:47,589
No! Dad!

438
00:37:47,948 --> 00:37:48,949
Dad!

439
00:37:49,248 --> 00:37:51,108
Why don't you ask your other son?

440
00:37:51,249 --> 00:37:53,708
Who really hurt Prince Tinnakorn?

441
00:37:55,244 --> 00:37:56,508
Phob! You shut up!

442
00:37:58,226 --> 00:38:00,148
Chat? What is going on?

443
00:38:04,428 --> 00:38:05,708
I got ambushed yesterday,

444
00:38:08,108 --> 00:38:10,228
Prince Tinnakorn saw it so he shieled me from the bullet.

445
00:38:10,860 --> 00:38:12,188
He saved my life.

446
00:38:20,628 --> 00:38:21,629
You did that?

447
00:38:23,490 --> 00:38:24,491
Huh?

448
00:38:24,668 --> 00:38:28,188
Chat? Did you try to kill him?

449
00:38:29,127 --> 00:38:31,268
He is lying, don't believe him.

450
00:38:31,314 --> 00:38:32,848
You're still denying it until now?

451
00:38:33,468 --> 00:38:35,028
This is so typical you,

452
00:38:35,308 --> 00:38:37,268
you're such a coward, so useless.

453
00:38:37,319 --> 00:38:38,470
Phob! You slave!

454
00:38:39,271 --> 00:38:40,868
What is going on?

455
00:38:41,308 --> 00:38:44,148
You two used to live together.

456
00:38:47,226 --> 00:38:48,516
I'm sorry, Your Highness,

457
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:50,148
for causing you some troubles.

458
00:38:52,268 --> 00:38:53,388
I should get going.

459
00:39:16,823 --> 00:39:18,388
What the hell did you do?

460
00:39:19,508 --> 00:39:20,988
Can't you just stay still?

461
00:39:21,703 --> 00:39:23,348
You want to go to jail?

462
00:39:24,194 --> 00:39:25,335
Have you ever thought that

463
00:39:25,567 --> 00:39:28,228
if Phob went to the police, what it will effect me?

464
00:39:29,708 --> 00:39:31,709
He attacked me first.

465
00:39:33,908 --> 00:39:35,628
He told his guys to hurt me.

466
00:39:36,065 --> 00:39:37,708
You expected me to do nothing?

467
00:39:38,388 --> 00:39:41,548
And let that slave stomp on my face for free?

468
00:39:42,268 --> 00:39:43,908
If you hadn't come to him first,

469
00:39:44,399 --> 00:39:46,000
if you hadn't hurt his mom,

470
00:39:46,028 --> 00:39:47,308
he wouldn't have attacked you like that.

471
00:39:48,348 --> 00:39:49,868
You are always causing troubles.

472
00:39:50,388 --> 00:39:52,670
You are always ruining the family's reputation.

473
00:39:53,698 --> 00:39:55,668
Why are you blaming me?

474
00:39:58,948 --> 00:40:00,668
I did all of that

475
00:40:01,666 --> 00:40:03,660
to teach them some lessons.

476
00:40:04,348 --> 00:40:06,668
So he would be scared and stopped the plan to transform the nation

477
00:40:06,678 --> 00:40:08,268
and transform the members of royal family like us.

478
00:40:11,943 --> 00:40:14,788
You've never seen anything good in me.

479
00:40:16,708 --> 00:40:19,108
I have never seen it because you have none!

480
00:40:19,709 --> 00:40:20,710
Chat!

481
00:40:21,198 --> 00:40:24,188
You are so useless to me!

482
00:40:26,199 --> 00:40:27,588
You're such a disgrace to me.

483
00:40:27,874 --> 00:40:29,148
You're so full of troubles.

484
00:40:31,875 --> 00:40:33,988
What had I done so wrong in my past lives?

485
00:40:34,060 --> 00:40:35,428
Why do I have you as a son?

486
00:40:37,528 --> 00:40:38,990
If I only had Tinnakorn as my only child,

487
00:40:39,082 --> 00:40:41,668
I wouldn't have had any bad headache for the rest of my life.

488
00:41:08,956 --> 00:41:10,988
What is going on?

489
00:41:11,826 --> 00:41:15,948
Why did Chat become such a cruel person?

490
00:41:16,866 --> 00:41:17,988
I wonder the same thing.

491
00:41:18,311 --> 00:41:20,468
Prince Chatthorn never liked Phob.

492
00:41:20,892 --> 00:41:23,308
But I don't think he would hate him enough to kill Phob.

493
00:41:24,556 --> 00:41:26,309
It was more than that.

494
00:41:27,508 --> 00:41:29,068
Did you see Vasin

495
00:41:30,567 --> 00:41:32,908
and his reaction to Phob?

496
00:41:34,327 --> 00:41:37,684
They acted as if they were enemies for such a long time.

497
00:41:38,220 --> 00:41:39,988
In the past,

498
00:41:40,595 --> 00:41:42,468
Vasin adored Phob.

499
00:41:43,068 --> 00:41:45,108
And Phob

500
00:41:45,988 --> 00:41:48,648
used to respect Vasin so much.

501
00:41:51,871 --> 00:41:52,948
Your Highness?

502
00:41:53,588 --> 00:41:55,668
Before Phob left the palace.

503
00:41:56,248 --> 00:41:59,548
Prince Chatthorn said that Phob sneaked in to see Prince Tinnakorn.

504
00:42:00,748 --> 00:42:02,048
After that,

505
00:42:02,819 --> 00:42:06,948
Prince Vasin forbade us from mentioning Phob.

506
00:42:07,988 --> 00:42:09,708
Do you think it would be related?

507
00:42:24,458 --> 00:42:25,459
How are you feeling?

508
00:42:26,932 --> 00:42:29,448
I'm fine, just a scratch on my arm.

509
00:42:39,933 --> 00:42:42,068
Why did you have to risk your life like that?

510
00:42:44,692 --> 00:42:46,668
I tried to protect Chat,

511
00:42:47,287 --> 00:42:48,948
protect our family.

512
00:42:50,198 --> 00:42:51,788
If something had happened to Phob,

513
00:42:52,028 --> 00:42:53,308
Chat would have been in big trouble.

514
00:42:55,655 --> 00:42:56,668
Are you sure about that?

515
00:42:59,623 --> 00:43:01,828
It wasn't because you still have feeling for him?

516
00:43:03,084 --> 00:43:04,868
And you could die to protect him?

517
00:43:10,188 --> 00:43:11,468
My feeling

518
00:43:11,989 --> 00:43:14,190
really doesn't matter here.

519
00:43:17,268 --> 00:43:19,308
When the celebration is over,

520
00:43:20,967 --> 00:43:24,420
Phob and I won't see each other again.

521
00:43:35,868 --> 00:43:38,388
Then I should leave you to rest.

522
00:43:40,351 --> 00:43:41,352
Dad?

523
00:43:46,500 --> 00:43:48,868
The celebration went smoothly and nothing happened.

524
00:43:50,297 --> 00:43:52,398
It meant that Phob had nothing to do with

525
00:43:52,508 --> 00:43:54,108
the regime change's team.

526
00:43:56,287 --> 00:43:57,668
Can I ask you

527
00:43:58,607 --> 00:43:59,848
to leave Phob alone?

528
00:44:00,431 --> 00:44:01,668
Stop monitoring him.

529
00:44:02,047 --> 00:44:04,108
We also should stop messing with him.

530
00:44:05,791 --> 00:44:07,068
We won't be in touch with him again.

531
00:44:08,548 --> 00:44:10,228
Can you do that for me?

532
00:44:43,364 --> 00:44:45,748
Fortunately, we didn't start our mission during the celebration.

533
00:44:46,588 --> 00:44:49,708
Otherwise, it would be bloodbath uprising for sure.

534
00:44:51,765 --> 00:44:53,788
We can't sit on it for too long.

535
00:44:54,100 --> 00:44:56,588
The longer we wait, the longer we give them time to plan.

536
00:44:59,288 --> 00:45:02,089
I think we shold take more time.

537
00:45:03,972 --> 00:45:06,468
We need to think and plan carefully.

538
00:45:06,988 --> 00:45:09,028
We still need information from all sources.

539
00:45:10,495 --> 00:45:11,668
Especially from you,

540
00:45:11,988 --> 00:45:12,989
Phobthee.

541
00:45:14,460 --> 00:45:16,708
You need to be around Prince Tinnakorn.

542
00:45:17,170 --> 00:45:19,748
The schedule from the royal secretary was useful to us.

543
00:45:22,268 --> 00:45:23,788
But the celebration was over.

544
00:45:24,828 --> 00:45:26,988
I don't think our path will cross again.

545
00:45:28,508 --> 00:45:31,588
Don't worry about your path with him.

546
00:45:32,448 --> 00:45:33,588
Give me a month,

547
00:45:34,628 --> 00:45:36,388
I will find a way to send you

548
00:45:36,828 --> 00:45:38,748
to work with Prince Tinnakorn

549
00:45:38,908 --> 00:45:40,708
in Royal Palace Office again.

550
00:46:01,940 --> 00:46:04,575
You feel bad for having to lie to Prince Tinnakorn again, don't you?

551
00:46:13,850 --> 00:46:14,932
During the celebration,

552
00:46:17,204 --> 00:46:19,548
- Prince Chatthorn tried to shoot me.
- What?

553
00:46:20,410 --> 00:46:21,628
Are you okay?

554
00:46:25,812 --> 00:46:26,813
Phob!

555
00:46:30,660 --> 00:46:32,268
Prince Tinnakorn was there to save me.

556
00:46:34,623 --> 00:46:36,468
He took a bullet for me.

557
00:46:39,412 --> 00:46:40,413
Janthorn.

558
00:46:42,516 --> 00:46:43,628
He saved my life.

559
00:46:46,516 --> 00:46:48,068
And now I have to use him again.

560
00:46:50,708 --> 00:46:51,748
I know

561
00:46:52,548 --> 00:46:55,268
- that you two were so close.
- Janthorn.

562
00:46:59,047 --> 00:47:01,388
I am so grateful for Prince Tinnakorn.

563
00:47:06,196 --> 00:47:08,308
He has never looked down on me even though I was only his servant.

564
00:47:12,185 --> 00:47:14,388
He made my life in the palace

565
00:47:15,548 --> 00:47:16,708
so happy and peaceful

566
00:47:21,258 --> 00:47:22,628
from his kindness.

567
00:47:28,378 --> 00:47:29,828
Look what I have to repay him,

568
00:47:31,724 --> 00:47:32,748
I'm a traitor.

569
00:47:33,980 --> 00:47:36,428
I betrayed him and I used him.

570
00:47:51,178 --> 00:47:52,179
Phob, listen to me.

571
00:47:53,716 --> 00:47:55,628
I understand that we put you in a tough position.

572
00:47:57,604 --> 00:47:59,428
But what we are doing right now

573
00:47:59,964 --> 00:48:01,448
is nothing personal.

574
00:48:03,383 --> 00:48:05,868
We are trying to transform the nation.

575
00:48:07,303 --> 00:48:08,428
We are doing this for people's rights

576
00:48:09,439 --> 00:48:11,786
and their freedom.

577
00:48:15,386 --> 00:48:16,588
- But I…
- Listen to me,

578
00:48:19,354 --> 00:48:21,108
about the royal family's schedule,

579
00:48:22,266 --> 00:48:24,588
I will ask my sources to look for it.

580
00:48:25,716 --> 00:48:26,908
If we can get one from my sources,

581
00:48:27,236 --> 00:48:29,028
you don't have to get anything out of Prince Tinnakorn.

582
00:48:32,607 --> 00:48:33,948
But if I can't get one,

583
00:48:36,308 --> 00:48:37,509
we need to rely on you.

584
00:48:47,484 --> 00:48:49,508
If he knows what we are doing,

585
00:48:52,551 --> 00:48:54,148
he will hate me for sure.

586
00:48:57,623 --> 00:48:59,028
You said it yourself

587
00:49:00,023 --> 00:49:02,228
that he has never looked down on anyone.

588
00:49:03,490 --> 00:49:05,708
He is a man with great vision.

589
00:49:06,911 --> 00:49:08,668
I believe that when the day has come,

590
00:49:09,764 --> 00:49:13,188
he will understand and forgive you.

591
00:49:27,764 --> 00:49:29,308
The archives for 150th anniversary of Rattanakosin celebration?

592
00:49:31,071 --> 00:49:32,072
Yes, Your Highness.

593
00:49:32,900 --> 00:49:35,868
The army sent me to work with the royal secretary department

594
00:49:36,676 --> 00:49:38,948
so that the archives will be accurate and complete.

595
00:49:43,151 --> 00:49:44,228
How is your wound?

596
00:49:46,770 --> 00:49:47,771
I feel so much better.

597
00:49:50,951 --> 00:49:54,348
But it's been only a month.

598
00:49:58,146 --> 00:49:59,147
And…

599
00:49:59,906 --> 00:50:02,628
many members of royal family are staying in Hua Hin, aren't they?

600
00:50:04,215 --> 00:50:05,908
I don't think there is anything urgent going on.

601
00:50:06,727 --> 00:50:07,748
You should have taken more days off.

602
00:50:08,572 --> 00:50:10,298
Even they are not staying in the city,

603
00:50:11,164 --> 00:50:13,388
there are still papers from various ministries that I need to care for.

604
00:50:15,969 --> 00:50:16,970
You're right.

605
00:50:20,780 --> 00:50:24,338
When are they coming back to the city?

606
00:50:25,756 --> 00:50:28,230
Are they staying at Klai Kangwong Palace for long?

607
00:50:30,068 --> 00:50:31,428
Why do you want to know?

608
00:50:38,335 --> 00:50:39,828
I should know their exact schedule

609
00:50:40,618 --> 00:50:43,628
so I can speed up on the archives when they return.

610
00:50:44,735 --> 00:50:46,948
This way, I don't have to disturb you when you're working.

611
00:50:57,812 --> 00:50:58,988
Captain Phobthee?

612
00:50:59,850 --> 00:51:02,068
Why are you here for?

613
00:51:10,340 --> 00:51:12,908
The prince and I are not strangers.

614
00:51:13,439 --> 00:51:14,948
I don’t have to visit him because of work merely,

615
00:51:15,839 --> 00:51:18,908
perhaps I can visit him when I miss him.

616
00:51:19,263 --> 00:51:20,388
The army sent

617
00:51:20,538 --> 00:51:22,148
him to work with me

618
00:51:22,239 --> 00:51:24,068
about the celebration's archives, Dad.

619
00:51:47,366 --> 00:51:48,367
You need to leave.

620
00:51:50,200 --> 00:51:51,360
You have to leave!

621
00:51:51,808 --> 00:51:53,500
Just go, get out of here!

622
00:51:53,560 --> 00:51:55,400
Why can't I run away from you?

623
00:51:55,461 --> 00:51:57,435
You're coming back, what did you expect me to do?

624
00:51:57,899 --> 00:52:00,280
How can I forget about you?

625
00:52:07,774 --> 00:52:10,040
The sources reported that the soldiers from our side were arrested.

626
00:52:10,060 --> 00:52:11,624
They will spill the members of this movement for sure.

627
00:52:11,640 --> 00:52:13,920
We need to do something to transform the nation soon.

